<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <SEO
    title="What Do Placement Agents Do? | Private Equity Fundraising Guide"
    description="Learn what placement agents do in private equity fundraising. Discover how PE placement agents connect fund managers with institutional investors and their key roles."
  />
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

